730
00:35:09,398 --> 00:35:10,482
He used a lawyer

731
00:35:10,608 --> 00:35:13,110
to periodically
provide him with inside information.

732
00:35:13,486 --> 00:35:15,362
Once he got
this information,

733
00:35:15,488 --> 00:35:18,281
