ingenious.

737
00:35:26,457 --> 00:35:28,542
If the trade was
ever under suspicion,

738
00:35:28,668 --> 00:35:30,210
even the trader
couldn't point to Bert.

739
00:35:30,336 --> 00:35:31,920
Okay. We've heard
more than enough. Thank you.

740
00:35:32,046 --> 00:35:34,714
