Because of this?

757
00:36:13,129 --> 00:36:14,546
I hope you're happy.

758
00:36:14,672 --> 00:36:16,923
Because without me,
this hedge fund is nothing.

759
00:36:17,049 --> 00:36:20,427
I'll be happy when the Department of
