760
00:36:20,553 --> 00:36:22,721
Enjoy your freedom, Bert,
because they're coming for you.

761
00:36:22,847 --> 00:36:25,932
And since you're a bigger trophy
than Gabriele Stone,

762
00:36:26,058 --> 00:36:28,935
