cheating for other people?

866
00:41:45,169 --> 00:41:47,170
Yes. I was helping
people cheat. Okay? But...

867
00:41:47,296 --> 00:41:48,713
But what?

868
00:41:56,472 --> 00:41:58,723
But it's not
the whole story.

